🆕 __Build Challenge__
:cluckshroom:Do you have a Cluckshroom or two? And how about all those regular chickens!? Let's give them a home. But not just any home. Show us your fanciest chicken coop for all your fancy (and not so fancy) chickens!
:air: 
:ChickenFace: **Chicken Coop Build Challenge- October 10th to October 24th**
:air: 
:paper: __Guidelines:__
:earth: Must be built in Minecraft Earth
:loading: This should be a brand new build and not be something that you've already built
:stonecutter_mc_animated:  Build plate size will not matter & won't be a factor in judging
:animMining:Feel free to ask for advice pertaining to your build in #build-challenge-chicken-coop
:mob_of_me: All work must be done by one individual
:fast_parrot: Remember, this is for fun only
📌If it's a submission picture, please feel free to ask a moderator to pin it
